  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub, not your words. NEEDS A HERO IMAGE: the hand-tracking visualization. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">Real-time 3D hand tracking using MediaPipe, OpenCV, and FastAPI, streaming hand position and rotation over WebSockets. It includes a cyberpunk visualization layer rendering the tracked hand.</p>\n<!-- NOTE (EJ): these shots are the \"Video Chord Controller\" tracking crows on a feeder cam (your Making Music With Crows piece) — same tracking→control pipeline. Move to its own project if you'd rather. -->\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Video Chord Controller tracking motion on a live feeder cam\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/handtrack-websockets/crows-1.png\" alt=\"Video Chord Controller tracking motion on a live feeder cam\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/handtrack-websockets/crows-1.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/handtrack-websockets/crows-1.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/handtrack-websockets/crows-1.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/handtrack-websockets/crows-1.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Video Chord Controller tracking motion on a live feeder cam\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1496\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2560×1496\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Video Chord Controller tracking motion on a live feeder cam</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Tracking vectors driving chords from crow movement\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://re